<body>
  <main>
    <article>
     

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Latest Tamil Movies Streaming on OTT Platforms</h2>
        <div class="movie-grid">
          <% tamMovies.forEach(movie => { %>
            <div class="card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Movie" aria-label="Details for <%= movie.title %>">
              <figure>
                <img src="<%= movie.poster %>" alt="<%= movie.title %> Tamil OTT movie poster" itemprop="image" loading="lazy">
              </figure>
              <h3 itemprop="name"><%= movie.title %></h3>
              <p><strong>OTT Release Date:</strong> <span itemprop="datePublished"><%= movie.ottReleaseDate || movie.releaseDate %></span></p>
              <p><strong>Streaming On:</strong> <span itemprop="provider"><%= movie.platform %></span></p>
              <div itemprop="actor" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <p><strong>Cast:</strong> <span itemprop="name"><%= movie.cast %></span></p>
              </div>
              <div itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <p><strong>Director:</strong> <span itemprop="name"><%= movie.crew %></span></p>
              </div>
              <p itemprop="description"><strong>Plot Summary:</strong> <%= movie.plot %></p>
              <p><a href="#" aria-label="Watch <%= movie.title %> on <%= movie.platform %>">Watch on <%= movie.platform %></a></p>
              <meta itemprop="genre" content="Tamil Cinema">
              <meta itemprop="url" content="https://ihalokam.vercel.app/movies/<%= movie.title.replace(/\s+/g, '-') %>">
            </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <p>The Tamil film industry, Kollywood, continues to captivate audiences in 2025 with its latest OTT releases, delivering a vibrant mix of blockbusters, dubbed films, and innovative storytelling. Streaming on platforms like Netflix, Disney+ Hotstar, Amazon Prime, and ZEE5, these Tamil OTT movies cater to diverse tastes. From action-packed thrillers to emotional dramas, here are six key aspects of the latest Tamil OTT releases, highlighting why they’re a must-watch.</p>
      </section>

